This comprehensive English localization file includes:
Extension metadata - Name, description, branding
Popup UI strings - Status messages, buttons, toggles, statistics
Overlay system - Sharingan/Madara EMS themed tooltips and menus
Settings pages - All 6 settings categories with detailed options
Error handling - Specific error messages for OCR, translation, network, license, and security issues
Notifications - System notification templates
Context menu - Right-click menu options
Cultural elements - Honorifics explanations and SFX (sound effects) translations
Time/duration formatting - Relative time strings
Units - Measurement abbreviations
The file follows i18n best practices with:
Interpolation placeholders ({count}, {version}, {date}, {percent}, {user})
Hierarchical organization matching the UI structure
Consistent terminology (Sharingan/EMS theme maintained throughout)
Accessibility considerations (high contrast, reduce motion options)
Cultural sensitivity (proper handling of Japanese honorifics and manga terminology)
